</head>
<body>
  <header></header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/start-team" class="btn btn-secondary back-button">← Back to Steps</a>
      <p class="step-label">Step 1 of 9</p>
      <h1>Find a Sponsor Organization</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Your FTC team needs a sponsoring school, club, community group, or nonprofit to register and compete.</p>

      <section class="content-section">
        <p>FTC teams need a responsible sponsor to provide oversight, facilities, and official registration support.</p>
        <div class="content-subsection">
          <h3>Typical sponsor options</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>School through a STEM, science, or technology department</li>
            <li>Community center or recreation program</li>
            <li>Boys &amp; Girls Club or similar youth organization</li>
            <li>Library or maker space with a STEM focus</li>
            <li>Nonprofit organization that supports robotics or education</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Action:</strong> Talk to a school administrator, club leader, or nonprofit coordinator about sponsoring your team.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="step-actions">
        <a href="/start-team-step2" class="btn btn-primary">Next: Get FIRST Involved →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script src="/assets/js/main.js?v=8"></script>
</body>
